{
  "analytics_identifier": null,
  "base_path": "/update-approved-driving-instructor-registration",
  "content_id": "72f03414-82e7-49e7-96c3-411afcc981ca",
  "description": "Update your personal details on the approved driving instructor (ADI) register and publish your details for learner drivers to see. ",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>Use this service to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>update your name or address on your approved driving instructor (<abbr title=\"approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr>) registration</li>\n  <li>agree to keep your professional skills up to date</li>\n  <li>agree to the <a href=\"/government/publications/driving-instructor-code-of-practice/approved-driving-instructor-adi-code-of-practice\"><abbr title=\"approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> code of practice</a>\n</li>\n  <li>publish your details on the <a href=\"/find-driving-schools-and-lessons\">find driving schools, lessons and instructors</a> service</li>\n  <li>view your standards check (previously called ‘check test’) history</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>This service is available from 6am to 11:30pm.</p>\n\n",
    "more_information": "<p>You need your:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>online user ID from the Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr>)</li>\n  <li>password</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"your-user-id-and-password\">Your user ID and password</h2>\n\n<p>You can find your user ID on letters you get from <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr>. It’s not the same as your <abbr title=\"approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> personal reference number.</p>\n\n<p>Email <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> if you’ve never had, or have lost, your user ID. You must include your:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n<abbr title=\"approved driving instructor\">ADI</abbr> personal reference number or driving licence number</li>\n  <li>date of birth</li>\n  <li>postcode</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>DVSA<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:customerservices@dvsa.gov.uk\">customerservices@dvsa.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<h3 id=\"rules-for-passwords\">Rules for passwords</h3>\n<p>You cannot use any of your 5 previously used passwords.</p>\n\n<p>Your password must be at least 9 characters long. It must include at least 3 of the following:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>uppercase characters, such as A B C</li>\n  <li>lowercase characters, such as a b c</li>\n  <li>numeric digits, such as 1 2 3</li>\n  <li>special characters, such as  £ % &amp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"help-with-updating-your-details\">Help with updating your details</h2>\n\n<p>Email <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> to get help updating your details online.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>DVSA<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:customerservices@dvsa.gov.uk\">customerservices@dvsa.gov.uk</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s a different process to <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://www.nidirect.gov.uk/contacts/contacts-az/driver-vehicle-agency-customer-services\">update your Northern Ireland ADI registration.</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://driver-services.dvsa.gov.uk/irdtm",
    "variants": [

    ],
    "will_continue_on": "the driving instructor service"
  },
